Standards-Version: 4.2.1
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10~), ocaml-best-compilers, ocaml (>= 4.02), camlp5, doc-base, dh-buildinfo, iso-codes, isoquery, po-debconf, liblablgtk2-ocaml-dev, ocaml-findlib
